cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.AI 

The paper deals with detecting changes in urban environments using remote sensing data, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a Siamese CNN for change detection suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves processing 3D point clouds, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR). The framework presented in the paper involves grouping and verifying object changes, which suggests a focus on robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the use of deep learning techniques for change detection suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
